snippet.title: Wild Pitch Ep 1 • Maybe: Interactive Stories
snippet.description:

Scenario by Jolly, RUKKIS.st | Artwork by Reum

You gave up on sports after an accident and vowed to focus only on your studies after you transfer. But you make an impression on Si-eon Park, captain and main catcher of the baseball team.
The captain keep asking you to be a pitcher.The man pitcher is wary yet helpful. The cleanup hitter strangely interested in you. Can you safely make it tograduation?
